  "descriptions": [
    {
      "text": "Namco Museum 64 is a compilation of several classic arcade games released by Namco, including Pac-Man, Ms. Pac-Man, Pole Position, Galaga, Galaxian and Dig-Dug. The game also features the ability to save high scores with the use of a Nintendo 64 Controller Pak. The N64 Rumble pack can also be used in with this game.",
